                     <binding notBefore="1400" notAfter="1500">
                        <p>White leather on boards, clasps lost, English 15th century work, with an extra cover of white leather, and a leather book-marker (Summary Catalogue). 'Original white leather binding on boards with chemise' (Pächt and Alexander)</p>
                        <p>Nailmarks at each corner and in the centre of the front cover; bosses formerly on each corner and in the centre of both covers 
